author: Juli Clover
title: watchOS 10.1 Fixes Apple Watch Weather Complication Bug
description: The watchOS 10.1 update that came out today fixes a bug that was causing Weather complications not to load properly on Apple Watch faces. First reported in September, the issue resulted in blank Weather complications even when the Weather app was working as i…
